Artist/Owner: 

Les Windley

munkybee503@yahoo.com



Les Windley's vision to fill a void in the constantly evolving tattoo community of Portland, Oregon cultivated in the creation of Nova Tattoo Studio. 

Founded in the summer of 2010, Nova Tattoo Studio is committed to offering customers a quality tattoo studio, where professionalism and hygiene are held to the highest standards. 

Our staff of trained tattooing professionals will guide you through each step of the process, as well as provide guidance on the care of your tattoo upon completion of the procedure. Your satisfaction and well-being is our highest priority. If you have a design that you would like us to facilitate on your behalf, stop by the studio and meet with one of our representatives for a quote. Kindly note that it's not our policy to provide tattoo quotes over the phone. 

For a better understanding of the services that we have to offer or if you have any questions, please contact us.

Remember the old saying: 

A good tattoo isn't cheap and a cheap tattoo isn't good!
